        <p>You're getting this mail because someone made an attempt to reset your password.</p>
        Click on the button below to get password reset page or manually copy this link to your browser <a href="<http://102.88.109.26:3000/users/password-reset/<%=user.token %>" target="_blank">http://102.88.109.26:3000/users/password_reset/<%=user.token %></a>
